I '''Juan Rulfo<ref>http://www.contactomagazine.com/rulfobio.htm</ref><ref>http://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juan_Rulfo#cite_ref-1</ref>''' ({{IPA-es|ˈxuan ˈrulfo}}) (16 Mayo1917 <ref>Ating e pamikasundu king aldo nang kebaitan Rufo. Agpang king kayang  [http://www.clubcultura.com/clubliteratura/clubescritores/juanrulfo/cronologia2.htm/ official web site] 1917 ya iti; nanupata, kaybat ning 1937, makalista ya ining 1918 uling e ustu ing binye nang banwa ba yang milub king military academy nung nu ya manibala ing bapa na. [http://www.utexas.edu/utpress/books/rulped.html] [http://www.literatura.us/rulfo/]  [http://www.library.txstate.edu/SWWC/WG/EXHIBITS/sacabo.html].</ref> &ndash; 7 Enero 1986) metung yang [[Mexico|Mexicanu]]ng talasulat, screenwriter ampong [[letratista]] o talakuang larawan. Metung ya kareng tatalangan dang diling talasulat king Latin America i Rulfo, at ing kayang reputasyon makasandal ya kareng adwang mangaimpis a libru, ing nobelang  ''[[Pedro Páramo]]'' (1955), ampo ing ''[[El Llano en llamas]]'' (1953), metung a koleksyon da reng makuyad a salita. Milikas la king Ingles deng labing lima (15) kareng labing pitung (17) kuwentung deti, at mibulalag la king pamagat a ''The Burning Plain and Other Stories''). Atyu king koleksyon a iti ing pupurian nang kuwentu, ing "¡Diles que no me maten!" ("Sabian Mu Karelang E Raku!"). Ya ampo i [[Jorge Luis Borges]] ing mepiling importanting diling talasulat king Castila king kaduang pulung dilanwa (''20th century'').

Ating maigit anam a libung ( 6,000) negative da reng kayang letratu king Katatagan Juan Rulfo  (''Juan Rulfo Foundation'').

